scripts.build: yarn clean && yarn build:esm && yarn build:cjs && node scripts/create-entrypoints.js && node scripts/check-tree-shaking.js
scripts.build:cjs: tsc --outDir dist-cjs/ -p tsconfig.cjs.json && node scripts/move-cjs-to-dist.js && rimraf dist-cjs
scripts.lint: eslint src && dpdm --exit-code circular:1 --no-warning --no-tree src/*.ts src/**/*.ts
